Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/kaya3/js3dgame

# Conflicts:
#	src/game.ts
#	src/main.ts
#	src/renderer.ts
#	src/scene-data.ts
Refactored RGB to Color, and added static methods to create a greyscale / rgb colour;
Added configuration options to allow changing of wasd vs arrow keys;
set background colour as config option; adjusted scene geometry;
cropped sprite image and fixed the coordinate at which the sprite gets drawn (defaults to top-left corner, but we want the bottom-left for the player image);
partial progress toward making drawing of sprite to be at the middle of the bottom edge of the sprite;
Sprite moves around the game, and is bounded by the walkable floor space #14 #17 #18 -- does not yet adjust z based on flooring, however (#16)
added point in polygon code (#15); refactored all "var" to "let";
